author:
Matt Buckler
Journal Inquirer
title: Starting at the end
text:
Journal Inquirer Journal Inquirer | 0 comments 
Most race drivers are approaching this weekend’s NAPA Fall Final at Stafford Speedway as the final race of the season. 
For Brian Sullivan of South Windsor, however, it’s opening day. He’s saying hello while everyone else is saying good bye.
